n style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">On9, 身邊有幾個中產人士本身都籌備左一段時間，想拎啲錢黎開黃店，壯大黃圈。<br />\n<br />\n佢地考慮左好耐，邊度搵個人名黎做商業登記證，因為一入左個名落去，基本上番唔到轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地都諗緊hold 一hold， 因為風險好撚大本身都唔緊要，但係一個有咩誤會，冇人會同你上法庭講證據，*跌*左落黃河就水洗都唔清。<br />\n好人仲會比人當賊辦，冇仇報。<br />\n<br />\n黃圈係要越大越好，成日話做唔到上游既黃圈，因為你都唔夠下游接貨，點樣比到一個利誘令上游生存到。<br />\n<br />\n下游要夠龐大，就要收納大量既商人願意用，願意表態。而家想淨係靠幾個政治名星開既黃店接？</span></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"95b313e31fc31f77f15dbb0d2168f50668f72b3e","tid":2059013,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"當大家仲係度內鬥嘅時候，麻煩你睇下流亡台灣嘅手足點講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059034</a>"},{"pid":"4884df3b88a8ac3c141541ed1e51fc16d14b2eef","tid":2059013,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a19888cce9d73e4d89dbc3a03cdf642a2202d1d","tid":2059013,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95d0621918c987048c8a07801ff68ff2dd8b8bc8","tid":2059013,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71ad3647b02938794805e64b839254e0d26c5552","tid":2059013,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"如果fb 見到有人又玩分化 麻煩幫手report<br />\n班狗好明顯㗎，全部like哂熱狗page"},{"pid":"182d659b9f0991e7569c07d0aa79b56f164a3d5a","tid":2059013,"uid":302140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:26:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"fd82b6bdaafa1e16b4e89b50c189afccfed72f59","tid":2059013,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d06f64ce286e8e8e498f45d2011f7853f531125","